Title: Find me
DateModified: '2019-03-11'
DatePublished: '2019-03-11'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/find-me
SetInCountry: Mexico
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Denisse  Sosa
AuthorCountry: Mexico
Text: This is me a 35 years old woman who suddenly question about her life and her
  doubts, truly i've done what i wanted? That's make me sad because i know in the
  deep of me that there is more beyond the words, beyond to be a mom a wife a daughter
  a friend!  i need to travel and find my real me that person who lose in the way
  that child who dreamed about to be great, i used to think my life is boring so easy
  but no my life is all less ordinary i've been sufer all my life i've been sick because
  of that i've been keep all my feellings and i am totally sure i want to share my
  experiences with everybody i want the people listen to me  i want the people reading
  to me so maybe my life change other lifes, i want my son is proud of me. I want
  to tell my story and heal my soul trough the words, that is the reason for what
  i want to know the world and im sure i want to travel and discovery what would have
  been different in my life.
